notes.note:
Good afternoon Louis, thank you for taking the time to speak with me earlier regarding the invoice for the work you had performed on your Tesla. As I mentioned to you over the phone, your contract covers you for the replacement of the rear drive unit oil pump, so we are going to reimburse you for this repair and the labour required to do the repair. Please note, items such as filters (and the labour to replace them), diagnostic fees, and fluids are not covered under your contract, so we will not be able to reimburse you for the costs associated with this portion of the invoice. Additionally, your contract covers you for a maximum of $130/h for labour, compared to Tesla's $210/h.
